{"id":172258,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/旧金山港区捷运因抗议而关闭移动网络/","date":"2011-08-15T13:00:14Z","modified":"2011-08-15T13:00:14Z","title":"旧金山港区捷运因抗议而关闭移动网络","content":"<p>当英国还在讨论是否在骚乱时关闭社交网站和移动通信时，旧金山的港区捷运（BART）为了防范可能的抗议而关闭了移动通信和网络。上个月，数百人在BART车站抗议7月3日的一次对峙中交通警察杀死了一名挥刀男子（视频），示威最后演变成了暴力。这家政府运行的运输公司在周五发布的一份声明中表示，公共场所受宪法第一修正案的保护，但在顾客付费的非公共场所，它有责任保护顾客和雇员的安全。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/17597469/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E6%B8%AF%E5%8C%BA%E6%8D%B7%E8%BF%90%E5%9B%A0%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E8%80%8C%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F08%2F13%2F086246%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E6%97%A7%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E6%B8%AF%E5%8C%BA%E6%8D%B7%E8%BF%90%E5%9B%A0%E6%8A%97%E8%AE%AE%E8%80%8C%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F08%2F13%2F086246%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/110621003576/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/17597469/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/110621003576/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/17597469/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=yF6lk1buz-M:iM4vhHl71xA:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=yF6lk1buz-M:iM4vhHl71xA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border